SCRIPT.MSCRI:
@echo off setlocal enabledelayedexpansion :INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.HEADER.PARAM_VALIDATION
:DEFINE &STRING_ARR#,string,30 :INC PCK.AUTOMIC_FILESYSTEM.PUB.INCLUDE.NORMALIZE_PATH "UC4RB_CONVERTED_STRING" = "UC4RB_TFS_UTIL_PATH" :INC PCK.AUTOMIC_FILESYSTEM.PUB.INCLUDE.NORMALIZE_PATH "UC4RB_CONVERTED_STRING" = "UC4RB_TFS_WORKING_DIR"
:SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "TF Utility Path" :INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.PARAM &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER_VAL# = &UC4RB_TFS_UTIL_PATH#
:SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "Workspace" :INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.PARAM &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER_VAL# = &UC4RB_TFS_WORKING_DIR#
:SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "Old Item" :INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.PARAM &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER_VAL# = &UC4RB_TFS_OLDITEM#
:SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "New Item" :INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.PARAM &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER_VAL# = &UC4RB_TFS_NEWITEM#
:SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "Version" :INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.PARAM &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER_VAL# = &UC4RB_TFS_VERSION#
:SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "Lock" :INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.PARAM &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER_VAL# = &UC4RB_TFS_LOCK#
:SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "No Get" :INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.PARAM &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER_VAL# = &UC4RB_TFS_NOGET#
set /a errors=0 > nul
:INCLUDE PCK.AUTOMIC_TFS.PRV.INCLUDE.ENSURE_UTILITY_PATH ! Check if TFS Utility Path exists :SET &UC4RB_CHECKME# = "&UC4RB_TFS_UTIL_PATH#" :INCLUDE PCK.AUTOMIC_FILESYSTEM.PUB.INCLUDE.CHECK_WINDOWS_CONSOLE_FILE_EXISTS
if %EXIST% == 0 ( : SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "TF Utility Path" : SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_ERROR# = "File &UC4RB_CHECKME# does not exist" : INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.ERROR.PARAMETER set /a errors=1 > nul ) else ( if %ISFILE% == 0 ( : SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "TF Utility Path" : SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_ERROR# = "&UC4RB_CHECKME# exist but is not a file" : INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.ERROR.PARAMETER set /a errors=1 > nul ) )
! Check if Workspace exists :SET &UC4RB_CHECKME# = "&UC4RB_TFS_WORKING_DIR#" :INCLUDE PCK.AUTOMIC_FILESYSTEM.PUB.INCLUDE.CHECK_WINDOWS_CONSOLE_FILE_EXISTS
if %EXIST% == 0 ( : SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "Workspace" : SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_ERROR# = "Directory &UC4RB_CHECKME# does not exist" : INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.ERROR.PARAMETER set /a errors=1 > nul ) else ( if %ISDIR% == 0 ( : SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_PARAMETER# = "Workspace" : SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_ERROR# = "&UC4RB_CHECKME# exist but is not a directory" : INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.ERROR.PARAMETER set /a errors=1 > nul ) )
if %errors% GTR 0 ( set retcode=%errors% goto :retcode )
:INC PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.HEADER.EXECUTION !Begin my code
!creates a branch :SET &UC4RB_TFS_COMMAND# = '"&UC4RB_TFS_UTIL_PATH#" branch "&UC4RB_TFS_OLDITEM#" "&UC4RB_TFS_NEWITEM#"'
:INCLUDE PCK.AUTOMIC_TFS.PRV.INCLUDE.HANDLE_VERSION_FLAG :INCLUDE PCK.AUTOMIC_TFS.PRV.INCLUDE.HANDLE_NOGET_FLAG :INCLUDE PCK.AUTOMIC_TFS.PRV.INCLUDE.HANDLE_LOCK_FLAG :INCLUDE PCK.AUTOMIC_TFS.PRV.INCLUDE.HANDLE_NOPROMPT_FLAG
:SET &UC4RB_LOGGING_INFO# = "Start branch ..." :INCLUDE PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.LOGGING.INFO cd /d "&UC4RB_TFS_WORKING_DIR#" :INCLUDE PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.CHECK_CMDLINE_CMD@WINDOWS &UC4RB_TFS_COMMAND# :INCLUDE PCK.ITPA_SHARED.PRV.INCLUDE.CHECK_CMDLINE_CMD@WINDOWS !End my code
